  "vlmDescription": "A Rhino viewport showing multiple SDF surfaces rendered by an in-process GLSL conduit. Up to 12 distinct 3D shapes visible simultaneously, grid-positioned: smooth spheres, a boolean union, TPMS lattices (gyroid with smooth triply-periodic surface, neovius with plate-like chambers), a twisted sphere, a driven gyroid, repeating spheres, a mesh-distance sphere, a VDB-voxelized sphere, a strut-foam network, a grid-based sphere, and a smooth-union blend. Some may be tiny or unframed. NOT an empty viewport."
 },
